  <description><![CDATA[<p>Holidays to <a data-udi="umb://document/c84fdc759cf240cb87b1070d34b08b4e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c84fdc759cf240cb87b1070d34b08b4e}" title="Calabria">Calabria</a> are packed full of culture and involve lots of beautiful beaches – so you’re in for a treat! We’ve planned a self-guided itinerary that takes you off the beaten track to the regions hidden gems, as well as making sure you visit the must see places. You’ll get to explore the stunning clifftop towns and villages, laze on pristine sandy beaches, try the fresh local produce at a rural farm and visit ancient buildings as you venture through this relatively undiscovered part of Italy.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/highlights-of-calabria#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/highlights-of-calabria#Itinerary&quot;">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/highlights-of-calabria#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/highlights-of-calabria#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/highlights-of-calabria#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
